data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION. Beautiful Property in Gibsonton, FL!! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2 bathroom home sitting on a generous lot measuring .69 acres  This is the ideal house for any family and is very centric near US Highway 41, lots of the commercial businesses , Brandon MALL , restaurants etc.   NO HOA FEES OR CDD. Owner willing to give $10k towards closing cost.    Don't miss out on this amazing property! Schedule your showing today!   Owner occupied, please do not disturb. Need appointment for showing with a 24 hr notice.
